          <h2>Dayananda Sagar University at AI Impact Summit 2026</h2>
          <p style="text-align:justify;">Dayananda Sagar University is proud to be part of the AI Impact Summit 2026, one of the most influential artificial intelligence gatherings in the Global South. As India’s AI-first University, DSU continues to lead meaningful conversations, foster global collaborations, and drive innovations that are shaping the future of Artificial Intelligence.
