		<div id="top8"  class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6" >
			
    
	
	<div class="module  " >
	    
		    <h3 class="modtitle">DSU DIFFERENTIATOR</h3>
	    
	    <div class="modcontent clearfix">
			
<style type="text/css">#yt_spotlight5 #top8 .module{
	margin-top: -30px
}</style>

<p class="diff">
<!-- START: Sliders -->
<div class="rl_sliders nn_sliders accordion panel-group" id="set-rl_sliders-1" role="presentation"><a id="rl_sliders-scrollto_1" class="anchor rl_sliders-scroll nn_sliders-scroll"></a>
<div class="accordion-group panel rl_sliders-group nn_sliders-group active">
<a id="rl_sliders-scrollto_curriculum" class="anchor rl_sliders-scroll nn_sliders-scroll"></a>
<div class="accordion-heading panel-heading" aria-controls="curriculum">
<a href="https://dsu.edu.in/index.php#curriculum" title="Curriculum" class="accordion-toggle rl_sliders-toggle nn_sliders-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" id="slider-curriculum" data-id="curriculum" data-parent="#set-rl_sliders-1" aria-expanded="true"><span class="rl_sliders-toggle-inner nn_sliders-toggle-inner"> <span style="color: #563993;">Curriculum</span></span></a>
</div>
<div class="accordion-body rl_sliders-body nn_sliders-body collapse in" role="region" aria-labelledby="slider-curriculum" aria-hidden="false" id="curriculum">
<div class="accordion-inner panel-body">
<h2 class="rl_sliders-title nn_sliders-title"><span style="color: #563993;">Curriculum</span></h2> Our curriculum is developed with our philosophy to quality education. Its salient features are that there is coherence in learning, it synthesizes experience and integrates education with experience. The curriculum is designed such that students get constant exposure to industry ready skills and techniques in conjunction with the theoretical fare that is on par with the best in the world.

</div></div></div>
<div class="accordion-group panel rl_sliders-group nn_sliders-group">
<a id="rl_sliders-scrollto_board-of-studies" class="anchor rl_sliders-scroll nn_sliders-scroll"></a>
<div class="accordion-heading panel-heading" aria-controls="board-of-studies">
<a href="https://dsu.edu.in/index.php#board-of-studies" title="Board of Studies" class="accordion-toggle rl_sliders-toggle nn_sliders-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" id="slider-board-of-studies" data-id="board-of-studies" data-parent="#set-rl_sliders-1" aria-expanded="false"><span class="rl_sliders-toggle-inner nn_sliders-toggle-inner"> <span style="color: #563993;">Board of Studies</span></span></a>
</div>
<div class="accordion-body rl_sliders-body nn_sliders-body collapse" role="region" aria-labelledby="slider-board-of-studies" aria-hidden="true" id="board-of-studies">
<div class="accordion-inner panel-body">
<h2 class="rl_sliders-title nn_sliders-title"><span style="color: #563993;">Board of Studies</span></h2> Every department is guided by a Board of Studies (BOS), with an eclectic mix of theoreticians and practitioners from the academia and industry. Each BOS is blessed with the brightest of minds from premier institutes like Indian Institute of Science (IISc); Indian Institute of Technology(IIT) and central research institutes. Almost all of our Board of Studies panel is headed by Professors from the Indian Institute of Science. 

</div></div></div>
<div class="accordion-group panel rl_sliders-group nn_sliders-group">
<a id="rl_sliders-scrollto_teaching-learning-process" class="anchor rl_sliders-scroll nn_sliders-scroll"></a>
<div class="accordion-heading panel-heading" aria-controls="teaching-learning-process">
<a href="https://dsu.edu.in/index.php#teaching-learning-process" title="Teaching Learning Process" class="accordion-toggle rl_sliders-toggle nn_sliders-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" id="slider-teaching-learning-process" data-id="teaching-learning-process" data-parent="#set-rl_sliders-1" aria-expanded="false"><span class="rl_sliders-toggle-inner nn_sliders-toggle-inner"> <span style="color: #563993;">Teaching Learning Process</span></span></a>
</div>
<div class="accordion-body rl_sliders-body nn_sliders-body collapse" role="region" aria-labelledby="slider-teaching-learning-process" aria-hidden="true" id="teaching-learning-process">
<div class="accordion-inner panel-body">
<h2 class="rl_sliders-title nn_sliders-title"><span style="color: #563993;">Teaching Learning Process</span></h2> We embrace the active learning paradigm for the delivery of our lectures. High quality lecture notes as part of the course pack based on the active learning paradigm have been developed exclusively by our faculty. Courses are delivered using our customization of MOODLE, DOODLE. PIAZZA is integrated into DOODLE to facilitate connection with the faculty beyond the classroom. Learning never stops at DSU. 

</div></div></div>
<div class="accordion-group panel rl_sliders-group nn_sliders-group">
<a id="rl_sliders-scrollto_industry-driven-academics-on-campus" class="anchor rl_sliders-scroll nn_sliders-scroll"></a>
<div class="accordion-heading panel-heading" aria-controls="industry-driven-academics-on-campus">
<a href="https://dsu.edu.in/index.php#industry-driven-academics-on-campus" title="Industry Driven Academics on Campus" class="accordion-toggle rl_sliders-toggle nn_sliders-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" id="slider-industry-driven-academics-on-campus" data-id="industry-driven-academics-on-campus" data-parent="#set-rl_sliders-1" aria-expanded="false"><span class="rl_sliders-toggle-inner nn_sliders-toggle-inner"> <span style="color: #563993;">Industry Driven Academics on Campus </span></span></a>
</div>
<div class="accordion-body rl_sliders-body nn_sliders-body collapse" role="region" aria-labelledby="slider-industry-driven-academics-on-campus" aria-hidden="true" id="industry-driven-academics-on-campus">
<div class="accordion-inner panel-body">
<h2 class="rl_sliders-title nn_sliders-title"><span style="color: #563993;">Industry Driven Academics on Campus </span></h2> Industry leaders like Autodesk, Bosch Etas, Bosch Rexroth, IBM, VMware, Nvidia and Intel have set up training academies on campus to train students from all over India in the latest technologies. Students at DSU benefit by being taking these certification courses, with possibilities for working on live research projects using them. 

</div></div></div>
<div class="accordion-group panel rl_sliders-group nn_sliders-group">
<a id="rl_sliders-scrollto_research" class="anchor rl_sliders-scroll nn_sliders-scroll"></a>
<div class="accordion-heading panel-heading" aria-controls="research">
<a href="https://dsu.edu.in/index.php#research" title="Research" class="accordion-toggle rl_sliders-toggle nn_sliders-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" id="slider-research" data-id="research" data-parent="#set-rl_sliders-1" aria-expanded="false"><span class="rl_sliders-toggle-inner nn_sliders-toggle-inner"> <span style="color: #563993;">Research</span></span></a>
</div>
<div class="accordion-body rl_sliders-body nn_sliders-body collapse" role="region" aria-labelledby="slider-research" aria-hidden="true" id="research">
<div class="accordion-inner panel-body">
<h2 class="rl_sliders-title nn_sliders-title"><span style="color: #563993;">Research</span></h2> With a plethora of doctorates from IITs, IISc. and TIFR, research at DSU compares with the best that India has to offer. Innovative research projects on Data Mining, Cloud Computing, Machine Learning, Signal Processing, Nano Materials and Devices, Thin Films, Composites design all offer a rich stimulating research environment. 

</div></div></div>
<div class="accordion-group panel rl_sliders-group nn_sliders-group">
<a id="rl_sliders-scrollto_faculty" class="anchor rl_sliders-scroll nn_sliders-scroll"></a>
<div class="accordion-heading panel-heading" aria-controls="faculty">
<a href="https://dsu.edu.in/index.php#faculty" title="Faculty" class="accordion-toggle rl_sliders-toggle nn_sliders-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" id="slider-faculty" data-id="faculty" data-parent="#set-rl_sliders-1" aria-expanded="false"><span class="rl_sliders-toggle-inner nn_sliders-toggle-inner"> <span style="color: #563993;">Faculty </span></span></a>
</div>
<div class="accordion-body rl_sliders-body nn_sliders-body collapse" role="region" aria-labelledby="slider-faculty" aria-hidden="true" id="faculty">
<div class="accordion-inner panel-body">
<h2 class="rl_sliders-title nn_sliders-title"><span style="color: #563993;">Faculty </span></h2> Our faculty are chosen after a rigorous selection process and many of them are from prestigious institutions in India and abroad. It is not uncommon to find PhDs from IITs and IISc teaching basic courses. What differentiates our faculty is the genuine empathy they have for their students. In the success of their students lies their satisfaction. 

</div></div></div>
<div class="accordion-group panel rl_sliders-group nn_sliders-group">
<a id="rl_sliders-scrollto_entrepreneurship" class="anchor rl_sliders-scroll nn_sliders-scroll"></a>
<div class="accordion-heading panel-heading" aria-controls="entrepreneurship">
<a href="https://dsu.edu.in/index.php#entrepreneurship" title="Entrepreneurship" class="accordion-toggle rl_sliders-toggle nn_sliders-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" id="slider-entrepreneurship" data-id="entrepreneurship" data-parent="#set-rl_sliders-1" aria-expanded="false"><span class="rl_sliders-toggle-inner nn_sliders-toggle-inner"> <span style="color: #563993;">Entrepreneurship</span></span></a>
</div>
<div class="accordion-body rl_sliders-body nn_sliders-body collapse" role="region" aria-labelledby="slider-entrepreneurship" aria-hidden="true" id="entrepreneurship">
<div class="accordion-inner panel-body">
<h2 class="rl_sliders-title nn_sliders-title"><span style="color: #563993;">Entrepreneurship</span></h2> A young individual now has the option to enter the portals of DSU to be trained as a professional Engineer in a selected domain or opt to become an Engineer-Entrepreneur. A good part of the 4 lakh sq. ft space in DSU's Campus 3, has the provision to accommodate about 200 enterprises offering all the needed support and facilities for an idea to be translated into a product. This is one of its kind initiative, exclusive at DSU. </div></div></div></div><!-- END: Sliders --></p>

	    </div>
	</div>
    
		</div>
		
		<div id="top9"  class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6" >
			
    
	
	<div class="module  feature-teachers " >
	    
		    <h3 class="modtitle">Leadership</h3>
	    
	    <div class="modcontent clearfix">
			
<div class="carousel-custommer"><div id="yt-extra-carousel" style="width:100%; height:100%" class="yt-extra-carousel carousel slide pull-center" data-ride="carousel" data-interval='false'><div class="carousel-inner"> <div class='item'>
<div class="customslider">
<div class="item-image"><img src="/images/demo/founder.jpg" alt="dayanandasagar" /></div>
<div class="content-main">
<h3 class="title">Late Shri R Dayananda Sagar</h3>
<span class="adred">Founding Father</span>
<p class="post-commnets">Our founding father, late Sri R Dayananda Sagar, was a graduate in Arts &amp; Commerce from India &amp; a barrister-at-law from England.</p>
<p> </p>
</div>
</div>
</div> <div class='item'>
<div class="customslider">
<div class="item-image"><img src="/images/demo/founder2.jpg" alt="chandrammasagar" /></div>
<div class="content-main">
<h3 class="title">Late Smt Chandramma Sagar</h3>
<span class="adred">Wife of the Founder</span>
<p class="post-commnets">Late Smt Chandramma Sagar was a doctor by profession, the first Indian woman to have acquired a triple fellowship from the Royal College of Surgeons (FRCS) from London, Edinburgh &amp; Glasgow.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div> <div class='item'>
<div class="customslider">
<div class="item-image"><img src="/images/demo/chancellor.jpg" alt="chancellor" /></div>
<div class="content-main">
<h3 class="title">Dr. D Hemachandra Sagar</h3>
<span class="adred">Chancellor</span>
<p class="post-commnets">Join me in taking the first steps as we set up the Dayananda Sagar University (DSU) that is backed by the legacy of Dayananda Sagar Institutions.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div> <div class='item'>
<div class="customslider">
<div class="item-image"><img src="/images/demo/prochancellor1.jpg" alt="prochancellor" /></div>
<div class="content-main">
<h3 class="title">Dr. D Premachandra Sagar</h3>
<span class="adred">Pro Chancellor</span>
<p class="post-commnets">DSU thus is now the most innovative –going beyond the teaching-learning, incubation, employment processes!</p>
</div>
</div>
</div> </div><a class="carousel-control left" href="#yt-extra-carousel" data-slide="prev"><i class="fa fa-angle-left"></i></a><a class="carousel-control right" href="#yt-extra-carousel" data-slide="next"><i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i></a><ol class="carousel-indicators" ><li data-slide-to="0" data-target="#yt-extra-carousel"></li><li data-slide-to="1" data-target="#yt-extra-carousel"></li><li data-slide-to="2" data-target="#yt-extra-carousel"></li><li data-slide-to="3" data-target="#yt-extra-carousel"></li></ol></div></div>

	    </div>
	</div>
    
